'''《外國公司問責法案》'''（{{lang-en|Holding Foreign Companies Accountable Act}}），是[[美國國會|美國國會]]一項要求在[[美國|美國]]證券交易所上市的公司聲明它們不是由任何外國政府擁有或控制的法案<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.marketwatch.com/story/senate-could-vote-on-bill-that-could-delist-chinese-companies-from-us-stock-exchanges-2020-05-19|title=Senate passes bill that could delist Chinese companies from U.S. stock exchanges|website=MarketWatch|date=2020-05-20|accessdate=2020-06-13|first=Chris|last=Matthews|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216223600/https://www.marketwatch.com/story/senate-could-vote-on-bill-that-could-delist-chinese-companies-from-us-stock-exchanges-2020-05-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它是《[[薩班斯-奧克斯利法案|薩班斯-奧克斯利法案]]》的修訂案，以要求這些公司向[[美國證券交易委員會|美國證券交易委員會]]披露妨礙[[上市公司會計監督委員會|上市公司會計監督委員會]]進行調查的海外司法管轄區資訊。若上市公司會計監督委員會連續三年未能對相關公司作出指定的審核報告，相關公司將被禁止交易及被撤銷上市地位<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2020/05/21/bill-that-could-delist-chinese-stocks-in-the-us-moving-at-warp-speed.html|title=Bill to delist Chinese stocks moving at ‘warp speed’ as a crackdown gains bipartisan support|website=CNBC|date=2020-05-21|accessdate=2020-06-13|first=Thomas|last=Franck|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117161934/https://www.cnbc.com/2020/05/21/bill-that-could-delist-chinese-stocks-in-the-us-moving-at-warp-speed.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==背景==
2019年，[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]][[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]][[美國參議院|美國參議院]]議員[[馬可·盧比奧|馬可·盧比奧]]曾就部份海外公司不遵守美國證券交易所的監督和審計規則提出《[[公平法案|公平法案]]》，以回應在美國證券交易所上市的中國大陸公司不合規和不透明，增加投資者被欺詐風險的問題<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-06-06/latest-u-s-salvo-against-chinese-firms-could-benefit-hong-kong|title=Latest U.S. Salvo Against Chinese Firms Could Benefit Hong Kong|last=Robertson|first=Benjamin|date=2019-06-06|work=Bloomberg News|access-date=2019-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190702024743/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-06-06/latest-u-s-salvo-against-chinese-firms-could-benefit-hong-kong|archive-date=2019-07-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《外國公司問責法案》在國會提出時，亦適逢中國大陸咖啡連鎖店[[瑞幸咖啡|瑞幸咖啡]]的財政醜聞被公眾關注。該公司的行政總裁及營運總監在2020年5月亦因涉嫌在2019年故意偽造3.1億美元的銷售額，導致瑞幸股價下跌約八成而被開除<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.axios.com/luckin-coffee-fires-ceo-coo-accounting-fraud-1ed86d90-fa65-4fe6-8c9b-1cae4b713b90.html|title=Luckin Coffee fires CEO and COO for fraud|website=Axios|date=2020-05-12|accessdate=2020-06-15|first=Dan|last=Primack|archive-date=2020-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022215452/https://www.axios.com/luckin-coffee-fires-ceo-coo-accounting-fraud-1ed86d90-fa65-4fe6-8c9b-1cae4b713b90.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。瑞幸也在2020年5月19日接獲[[納斯達克|納斯達克]]的退市通知<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.axios.com/luckin-coffee-nasdaq-fraud-028c32e7-e283-415c-96b5-30c4b19f5158.html|title=Luckin Coffee faces Nasdaq delisting following alleged fraud|website=Axios|date=2020-05-20|accessdate=2020-06-15|first=Dan|last=Primack|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031144406/https://www.axios.com/luckin-coffee-nasdaq-fraud-028c32e7-e283-415c-96b5-30c4b19f5158.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。6月26日，瑞幸從納斯達克退市，當天為該公司股票的最後一個交易天<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.marketwatch.com/story/luckin-coffee-to-be-delisted-from-the-nasdaq-2020-06-26|title=Luckin Coffee to be delisted from the Nasdaq|website=MarketWatch|date=2020-06-26|accessdate=2020-06-27|first=Tonya|last=Garcia|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126090518/https://www.marketwatch.com/story/luckin-coffee-to-be-delisted-from-the-nasdaq-2020-06-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==立法歷程==
2020年5月20日，該法案獲得美國參議院一致同意通過<ref>{{Cite web|last=Matthews|first=Chris|title=Senate passes bill that could delist Chinese companies from U.S. stock exchanges|url=https://www.marketwatch.com/story/senate-could-vote-on-bill-that-could-delist-chinese-companies-from-us-stock-exchanges-2020-05-19|access-date=2020-12-03|website=MarketWatch|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216223600/https://www.marketwatch.com/story/senate-could-vote-on-bill-that-could-delist-chinese-companies-from-us-stock-exchanges-2020-05-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年12月2日，該法案再獲得[[美國眾議院|美國眾議院]]口頭表決通過<ref>{{Cite news|last=Zengerle|first=Patricia|date=2020-12-03|title=Chinese firms on U.S. exchanges threatened by bill headed to Trump's desk|language=en|agency=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-china-stocks-idUSKBN28C3C3|access-date=2020-12-03|archive-date=2020-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208223818/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-china-stocks-idUSKBN28C3C3|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

